{"tid":586714,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"葉蔚琳與丈夫劉卓恒獲九巴派更　恢復駕車","createTime":"2018-03-09T18:39:18.000Z","updateTime":"2018-03-09T21:52:02.000Z","uid":79563,"like":0,"dislike":5,"uniUserReply":9,"replies":[{"pid":"f3a69daae2090eeb573ca95ed9d4d5e55ae4987f","tid":586714,"uid":79563,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-03-09T18:39:18.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"http://newsstatic.rthk.hk/images/mfile_1384965_1_L_20180309202657.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=http%3A%2F%2Fnewsstatic.rthk.hk%2Fimages%2Fmfile_1384965_1_L_20180309202657.jpg&h=7fb03058&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n被九巴暫緩終止僱用的月薪車長大聯盟召集人葉蔚琳，及她的丈夫劉卓恒，透過傳媒通訊群組表示，獲九巴安排派更，今日負責234X路線。<br />\n<br />\n九巴早前向4名車長發出解僱通知信，翌日暫緩有關決定。4人正透過上訴機制，覆檢解公司決定。"},{"pid":"20d04e7fd65988cf04921c948de13fbac7dc8b51","tid":586714,"uid":22974,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-03-09T20:06:17.000Z","msg":"此回覆已被刪除"},{"pid":"d1ea9eb061f5059f80209077e7cdf66a01227ef9","tid":586714,"uid":15984,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-03-09T20:09:41.000Z","msg":"掛著番工而唔抗爭<br />\n實比連登仔屌撚到傻"},{"pid":"bfce8a22418c9a91c179b16273cd5cc98ea1b3d8","tid":586714,"uid":128219,"like":1,"dislike":2,"score":-1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-03-09T20:33:02.000Z","msg":"此回覆已被刪除"},{"pid":"1818902312fedab539651af7dad35cee88f5b466","tid":586714,"uid":4575,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-03-09T20:39:44.000Z","msg":"九巴炒左個HR未？ 究竟而家個HR做錯定啱"},{"pid":"d52dd79d9978acd73337e3604ae6ce834ca4689e","tid":586714,"uid":43575,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-03-09T21:03:21.000Z","msg":"狗巴當佢兩公婆係狗咁撚，炒完又請請完又炒 無限loop"},{"pid":"32329e1ed53fe6e09433ad85e3d84d2f70c3e5fc","tid":586714,"uid":12034,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-03-09T21:38:36.000Z","msg":"又咪向惡勢力低頭<br />\n<br />\n有骨氣就唔撈啦 <img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/hehe.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/hehe.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"